## Production Readiness Review Areas

The checklist must include all of the following areas (with pass/fail/blocked/N-A per item):

### 1. DNS Ownership
- All prod DNS records have documented owners
- No unowned DNS records
- DNS ownership matrix reviewed and current (Phase 10 / earlier)
- DNS scan passed in last 7 days

### 2. Tunnel Runtime Ownership
- Active tunnel ID documented
- Tunnel ingress hostnames match runtime
- No orphaned credential files unaddressed
- Tunnel runtime config matches repo intent
- Cloudflared service running (read-only status check)

### 3. Worker Route Ownership
- All prod Worker routes documented with owners
- No route overlap detected
- Worker routes match Terraform intent
- Worker routes tagged with environment: prod

### 4. AI Gateway Governance
- All AI Gateway routes documented
- KV/D1/R2 bindings documented
- Binding ownership assigned
- No undocumented bindings

### 5. KV / D1 / R2 Bindings
- All bindings inventoried
- No stale or orphaned bindings
- Bindings documented with owner and purpose

### 6. Terraform Ownership
- All Cloudflare Terraform resources have owners
- State matches documentation intent
- No drift detected (or drift documented with SLA)
- Backend configuration is a single valid backend (no duplicate blocks)

### 7. Secret Containment
- No secrets committed to repository
- No tokens found in tracked files
- Secret scan passed (gitleaks or equivalent)
- Credential files are outside repository

### 8. CI Enforcement
- All CI gates active and passing
- Shellcheck passing
- Validation scripts passing
- No workflow policy violations

### 9. Risk Scoring
- Phase 17 risk score completed for this change
- Aggregate risk level documented
- Required approvals obtained per risk level
- Evidence scorecard in archive

### 10. Environment Separation
- Dev/staging/prod boundaries verified (Phase 18)
- No prod domains in dev/staging configs
- Environment YAML files reviewed

### 11. Disaster Recovery
- DR tabletop completed for applicable scenarios (Phase 19)
- Recovery ownership matrix current
- Restore evidence template available

### 12. Rollback Plan
- Rollback plan documented (Phase 12/13)
- Rollback owner identified
- Rollback steps tested or reviewed
- Break-glass procedure available if needed

### 13. Evidence Archive
- Change record opened in evidence archive (Phase 16)
- CI report captured
- Baseline diff captured
- Release approval form completed

### 14. Owner Sign-Off
- All required owners have signed off
- Review board quorum met (if High/Critical risk)
- Sign-off evidence in archive

---

## Required Deliverables

### Documentation Files

1. **`docs/infra/cloudflare-production-readiness-review.md`**
   - Overview of production readiness framework
   - How this review links to all prior phases (10–19)
   - When this review is required
   - Who conducts the review
   - What blocks a go decision

2. **`docs/infra/cloudflare-production-readiness-checklist.md`**
   - All 14 areas above with full checklist items
   - Each item has: status field `[ ] PASS / FAIL / BLOCKED / N-A` | evidence reference | owner
   - Summary section: total PASS / FAIL / BLOCKED count
   - Final decision field: GO / NO-GO / CONDITIONAL

3. **`docs/infra/cloudflare-production-go-no-go-template.md`**
   - Change ID
   - Change description
   - Risk level (from Phase 17)
   - Environment
   - Checklist summary (pass/fail counts)
   - Blocking items (list)
   - Conditional items (list)
   - Decision: GO / NO-GO / CONDITIONAL
   - Decision rationale
   - Approver sign-off fields
   - Evidence archive reference

4. **`docs/infra/cloudflare-rollback-readiness-checklist.md`**
   - Pre-change rollback readiness:
     - Rollback plan documented? (Phase 12)
     - Break-glass procedure available? (Phase 13)
     - Rollback owner identified?
     - Rollback steps reviewed?
     - Rollback evidence template ready (Phase 19)?
   - Post-change rollback verification:
     - Change applied successfully?
     - Rollback still possible if needed?
     - Evidence captured?

5. **`docs/infra/cloudflare-drift-report.md`** *(update)*
   - Add `production_readiness_status` field per drift item
   - Cross-reference Phase 20 checklist

6. **`infra/cloudflare/README.md`** *(update)*
   - Add Phase 20 entry with links to all deliverables above

